{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, though DWT enriches the feature representation due to the involved spatial and frequency-domain information, extra processing may challenge real-time applications, especially in resource-constrained clinical settings.",
    "This framework also suffers from another point: complete reliance on the manual hyper-parameter finetuning of CNNs, DWT, and SVM.",
    "Though these hyper-parameters were optimized for the CKHK-22 dataset, they are open to reoptimization over other datasets, which may affect the reproducibility and scalability of the model.",
    "Moreover, this study does not comment on how rare or edge cases could affect both classification and segmentation tasks.",
    "The lack of extensive external validation using various independent datasets restricts the validation of the framework in more general clinical scenarios."
  ]
}